{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLShadowElement","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLShadowElement","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLShadowElement\"><code>HTMLShadowElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLShadowElement/getDistributedNodes\"><code>getDistributedNodes()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Components</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry\"><code>CustomElementRegistry</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document/createElement\"><code>Document.createElement()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/attachShadow\"><code>Element.attachShadow()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/shadowRoot\"><code>Element.shadowRoot</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/slot\"><code>Element.slot</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/composed\"><code>Event.composed</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/composedPath\"><code>Event.composedPath</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement\"><code>HTMLSlotElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>Node.getRootNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node/isConnected\"><code>Node.isConnected</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot\"><code>ShadowRoot</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/customElements\"><code>Window.customElements</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard obsolete\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Obsolete:</strong> This feature is obsolete. Although it may still work in some browsers, its use is discouraged since it could be removed at any time. Try to avoid using it.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>A interface&nbsp;<code><strong>HTMLShadowElement</strong></code>&nbsp;representa um &nbsp;elemento HTML&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, Ao qual é usado no <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_shadow_DOM\">Shadow DOM</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Propriedades","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>&nbsp;Esta interface herda as propriedades do&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a>.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"métodos","title":"Métodos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Esta interface herda os métodos do&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a>.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmlshadowelement.getdistributednodes_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLShadowElement/getDistributedNodes\"><code>HTMLShadowElement.getDistributedNodes()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Retorna uma estática&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a> do&nbsp;<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\">distributed nodes</a> associado com este elemento &lt;shadow&gt;.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"spec-table standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/webcomponents/spec/shadow/#the-shadow-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Shadow DOM<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'shadow' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLShadowElement","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLShadowElement/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Se Shadow DOM não é habilitado no Firefox, os elementos &lt;shadow&gt; se comportarão como&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Shadow DOM foi implementado primeiro no Firefox 28 e está por trás de uma preferência,&nbsp;<code>dom.webcomponents.enabled</code>, ao qual é desabilitado por padrão. [1]</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>O elemento HTML <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> , implementa esta interface.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_shadow_DOM\">Shadow DOM</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect2\">&nbsp;</dt>\n</dl>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Propriedades","id":"properties"},{"text":"Métodos","id":"métodos"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"A interface HTMLShadowElement representa um  elemento HTML <shadow> (en-US), Ao qual é usado no Shadow DOM.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLShadowElement","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLShadowElement","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"HTMLShadowElement","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLShadowElement","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/htmlshadowelement","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/htmlshadowelement/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLShadowElement","title":"HTMLShadowElemen